rents.title: the starling
rents.description: Breathtaking walk-out triplex located in desirable Waterloo. The 2500 square foot home features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, with plenty of room to grow. The bedrooms are all large, with 2 on the main floor and 2 upstairs. The main floor features a spacious living space with a gas fireplace, large kitchen with plenty of cupboards and storage, and a deck overlooking the back yard. There is also a one bedroom basement suite that is currently rented for $1100 per month. The exterior has been well maintained and includes a detached garage, concrete patio, and private back yard. This home is perfect for an owner occupied family or an investor looking for a great investment opportunity. It is located in a great neighbourhood close to schools, parks, community center and shopping areas.

rents.title: Villa d'Espagne
rents.description: This beautiful, spacious and bright 3 Bedroom and 2 Bathroom house for rent is located at 1366 Bizerte Street, Bizerte, LA. With an open floor plan and spacious kitchen, you'll find it difficult to find a nicer home at this price! The living room features a large window and a fireplace perfect for those chilly winter evenings. The master bedroom is spacious with bath, walk-in closet and television hook-up. The master bathroom has dual sinks and a separate toilet area as well as a large shower with bench and plenty of storage. There is also a half bath on the first floor. This home includes an attached carport and an extra deep driveway for parking extra vehicles. Contact us now to book a viewing!

agencies.description: Bizerte Findstate est une entreprise qui gère les transactions immobilières de ses clients, de la mise en vente de biens à la gestion locative, en passant par l’estimation ou la recherche de biens. Ses collaborateurs sont généralement des agents immobiliers ou des agents commerciaux. L’agence immobilière fait le lien entre les offreurs de biens (vendeurs) et les demandeurs de biens (les acheteurs ou les locataires).
